{"tid":1895842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪應該幫下韓仔？入黎畀啲意見","createTime":"2020-02-24T19:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T07:28:39.000Z","uid":323918,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1cdf4b0d45e8dcfd5a17efedd6fc57b7fe0708ba","tid":1895842,"uid":323918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"老實，韓仔係好撐我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做過好多嘢，唔知就自己google 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n韓仔係手足（大部分掛）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩我地都未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以幫到嘅係錢同其他物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個睇法係，我地有韓國嘅導演朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係搞，可以搵導演幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁做係要畀韓仔知道，我哋香港人唔會忘記過去半年黎嘅支持。當然仲有其他，明就明"},{"pid":"44648eac51ac5b576acb78cb5da4bdc036eee087","tid":1895842,"uid":323918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:01:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78768af570a8988ec10312577ee4e969baedc657","tid":1895842,"uid":323918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4927a322e1c7e02db819249663fd9baeb58b095","tid":1895842,"uid":323918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bc2dbb8658884e141a3ce55ab8a0603d110cde","tid":1895842,"uid":323918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b156f1aa06